    "description": "SHARECARE https://www.sharecare.com\n\nFULL-STACK DEVELOPER PYTHON\n\nDescription\n\nWe are seeking an experienced backend Python developer with expertise in building and extending our API on Django Rest Framework. Your primary responsibility will be to develop and maintain new modules for consumer and internal facing applications. In addition, you will need to coordinate with the rest of the team working on different layers of the applications. A commitment to collaborative problem-solving, sophisticated design, and quality product is essential.\n\nRequirements\n\n - At least 4 years of practical experience in building web applications\n\n - Strong proficiency with Python, Django Rest Framework\n\n - Excellent command over Data structure and Algorithms\n\n - Must demonstrated efficient use of AI tools in development\n\n - Proficient in working with SQL and NoSQL database solutions such as PostgreSQL\n\n - Previous experience with popular libraries such as mock, pytest\n\n - Proficiency in the English language, both written and verbal, sufficient for success in a remote and largely asynchronous work environment.\n\n - Proficient using code versioning tools such as Git\n\n - Proficient working with dockerized applications\n\nResponsibilities\n\n - Develop and maintain existing legacy or new applications\n\n - Ensure the best possible performance, quality, and responsiveness of applications.\n\n - Analyzing requirements and designing new functionality.\n\n - Identify bottlenecks and bugs, and devise solutions to mitigate and address these issues.\n\n - Leverage AI tools into their workflow to maintain efficiency\n\nSelection Process\n\n - Recruiter Screen\n\n - Live Coding Interview\n\n - Client Screening Interview\n\n - Client Technical Interview\n   ",
